[to the ticket seller at the arena]
I see you're positively psychic, Mac. Why don't you get yourself a crystal ball and call yourself "Madame Knowsall?"

[to Maris]
You're awful sober to be a reporter, aren't you?
You go to the movies too, hunh?
Why did you have to make a shooting gallery out of my place?

[to Maris]
Young lady, when you and I get to the hospital, we;re gonna have a talk - man-to-man!
